headline: Northern Trust Corporation (NTRS) Q3 Earnings Top Estimates
summary: Northern Trust (NTRS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +1.33% and -0.76%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
